OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Travellers on an intercity train in    
OL,6, Austria were startled on Sunday when a 
OL,7, recording of an Adolf Hitler speech was
OL,8, played on board.                       
OL,10,FInstead of the normal announcements, a 
OL,11,Fcrowd could also be heard shouting     
OL,12,F"Heil Hitler" and "Sieg Heil" over the 
OL,13,Ftrain's speaker system.                
OL,15,FThe operator said there had been       
OL,16,Fseveral such incidents in recent days. 
OL,18,FOne passenger on the Bregenz-Vienna    
OL,19,Fservice told the BBC that everyone on  
OL,20,Fthe train was "completely shocked".    
